# Testing

## Unit Tests
- `#[cfg(test)] mod tests` in same file as implementation
- `use super::*` and `use crate::...` for imports

```rust
#[cfg(test)]
mod tests {
    use super::*;
    use crate::models::shared::TrackIdentifier;

    #[test]
    fn pattern_seq_can_be_created() { ... }
}
```

## Integration Tests (UI)
- Emulator pattern: struct holding `&mut MainWindow`, helper methods (`click`, `click_menu_item`, `tracks_present`)
- Use `iced_test` simulator for `find`, `click`, `into_messages`
- Handle async engine updates: `thread::sleep` + `data_change_receiver.try_recv` in `process_messages`

## Test Helpers
- `assert_approx_eq!` macro for float comparisons in audio tests
- Mock implementations (e.g., `MockInput` impl `Output`) for audio pipeline tests
